MapReduce for Stampede
======================

A C++ framework by Sai Avala and Sudheesh Katkam

In mapreduce dir,

On Stampede idev session:
$ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/work/00434/eijkhout/boost/installation/lib
$ make matrix
$ ibrun matrix.out

On Mac:
$ make matrix
$ mpirun -np 4 matrix.out

Boost MPI Library:
http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_55_0/doc/html/mpi.html

Google's MapReduce Paper:
http://static.googleusercontent.com/media/research.google.com/en/us/archive/mapreduce-osdi04.pdf
